						               													<description>Company of Liars [COL] is a strategic card game with a board. It is a game for two persons and it is set in the gloomy times of World War II. The aim of each player is to collect 60 points, to take control of key points, or simply to destroy their enemy!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the moment there are four factions: the USA, Germany, the United Kingdom and the Resistance.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players conceal their troops on a map where companies are formed. These companies will then assault their foes. Each unit has its specific abilities so merging units will increase their power and augment their flexibility which is crucial for gaining the upper hand over your enemy!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Equally important elements of the game are managing your supply of commands that will allow you to perform actions, gathering information about the enemy and last but not least.. skilful bluffing!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The company of Liars awaits you!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
